platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From the second Barry Steakfries busts through that laboratory wall, Jetpack Joyride thrusts you into an unforgettable horizontal adventure. This stylish infinite runner gets your pulse pounding as you feverishly snag coins, dodge obstacles and take rides in crazy vehicles (think: robotic dragons and money-propelled birds). It’s a classic that’s only gotten better over the years, thanks to Halfbrick Studios' consistent updates.

From the second Barry Steakfries busts through that laboratory wall, Jetpack Joyride thrusts you into an unforgettable horizontal adventure. This stylish infinite runner gets your pulse pounding as you feverishly snag coins, dodge obstacles, and take rides in crazy vehicles (think: robotic dragons and money-propelled birds). It’s a classic that’s only gotten better over the years, thanks to Halfbrick Studios' consistent updates.

Enfilez votre jetpack afin d’échapper à la horde de scientifiques, de missiles et de faisceaux laser qui se dresse sur votre chemin. À l’aide de vaisseaux plus déjantés les uns que les autres, amassez le maximum de pièces et tenez la distance dans ce jeu de course infinie tenace, créé pour votre plus grand amusement par les studios Halfbrick.
從主角 Barry Steakfries 破牆衝入實驗室的那一刻起，《Jetpack Joyride》就把玩家拉進一場刺激難忘的冒險旅程。在這款充滿設計感的橫向跑酷遊戲中，無論是拼命吃金幣、閃躲障礙物或是騎乘各式新奇飛行器（像是機器巨龍或靠金幣驅動的噴射鳥），都能享受到高速脈搏衝擊的快感。這款遊戲堪稱經典佳作，而且開發商 Halfbrick Studios 不斷推陳出新，讓遊戲歷久彌新。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Brilliant controls and loads of fun power-ups that don't fade with age.
